Eskom is immensely encouraged by the way in which the Steve Tshwete Local Municipality manages their Eskom account payments. They always pay their monthly accounts in full and on time. We appreciate the fact that the municipality honours their account payments and we embrace the good relationship with them said Musa Mabila, Senior Manager Customer Service Operations (acting), Mpumalanga.Municipal customers are encouraged to engage with their supply authorities to get updated information on their municipalities accounts.